    <item>
      <title>谷歌开始在人工智能概览搜索结果中广泛推出广告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/google-begins-wide-rollout-of-ads-in-ai-overview-search-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc. 旗下的谷歌正在广泛推出广告，这些广告将显示在某些搜索结果顶部的人工智能生成的摘要内和旁边——此举旨在向投资者展示昂贵的人工智能项目可以创造收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/google-begins-wide-rollout-of-ads-in-ai-overview-search-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 在 66 亿美元融资基础上再获 40 亿美元信贷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/openai-gets-4-billion-in-credit-on-top-of-6-6-billion-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 在最近筹集的 66 亿美元资金基础上，又从全球银行获得了 40 亿美元的循环信贷额度，积累了庞大的资金，以在开发更复杂人工智能的昂贵竞赛中保持领先地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/openai-gets-4-billion-in-credit-on-top-of-6-6-billion-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 14:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约学校因家长反对而撤销手机禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nyc-schools-reverse-course-on-cell-phone-ban-after-parents-balk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市教育局长戴维·班克斯 (David Banks) 表示“现在还不是”在学校禁止使用手机的时候，他提到了上个月上西区两所学校封锁期间家长难以联系到孩子这一担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nyc-schools-reverse-course-on-cell-phone-ban-after-parents-balk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:28:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Visa 推出平台帮助银行在全球范围内发行稳定币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/visa-launches-platform-to-help-banks-issue-stablecoins-globally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着越来越多的金融机构和企业对加密货币和区块链技术如何改善其运营表现出兴趣，Visa Inc. 正在推出一个供银行发行法定支持的代币（如稳定币和代币化存款）的平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/visa-launches-platform-to-help-banks-issue-stablecoins-globally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:15:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电推出单一股票 ETF，Direxion 基金允许杠杆投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/tsmc-gets-single-stock-etf-as-direxion-funds-allow-leverage-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Direxion Funds 推出了两只专注于一只新兴市场股票 — — 台湾半导体制造股份有限公司 — — 的交易所交易产品，允许投资者对其做超额看涨押注，或采取与市场走势相反的仓位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/tsmc-gets-single-stock-etf-as-direxion-funds-allow-leverage-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:11:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PayPal 使用稳定币完成首笔商业交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/paypal-completes-its-first-business-transaction-using-stablecoin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PayPal Holdings Inc. 使用其专有的稳定币完成了首笔商业支付，以展示如何使用数字货币来改善通常笨拙的商业交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/paypal-completes-its-first-business-transaction-using-stablecoin</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾股市休市两天后恢复交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/taiwan-to-resume-stock-market-trading-after-two-day-closure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾股市和货币市场在因台风“克拉通”关闭两天后，将于周五恢复交易，届时股市和货币市场可能将迎头赶上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/taiwan-to-resume-stock-market-trading-after-two-day-closure</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 12:05:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 募集 66 亿美元资金，估值达 1570 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/openai-has-closed-new-funding-round-raising-over-6-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 已完成一项筹集 66 亿美元新资金的交易，使这家人工智能公司的估值达到 1570 亿美元，并加强了其打造全球领先的生成式人工智能技术的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/openai-has-closed-new-funding-round-raising-over-6-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 16:18:42 GMT</pubDate>
